entries.entry: We learned about automating HTML representations and event listeners. The power generator then blew up, providing convenient cover for my escape from this hellish abyss.
We learned how to use GitHub on a team and finished our first group project. It was difficult but rewarding to learn so many new valuable things, and I came away with a great sense of achievement.
Things are now in motion that cannot be undone.
this is not a drill ladies and gents
